\chapter{The Avrani}
\section{Description}

The Avrani are a race who's existence is known of only because of 
occasional spacecraft sightings and a few deceased Avrani found 
destroyed by Yis'Daak hunters. 

Standing less than 1.2 Meters they are a very physically 
unthreatening race. They are also the most technologically advanced 
of all the cultures with and average tech level of 16. 

